I am overriding Renderers with my own, for example:

```
[assembly: ExportRenderer(typeof(Xamarin.Forms.Label), typeof(MyProjLabelRenderer))]
namespace MyProj.Droid.CustomRenderers.Controls
{
    public class MyProjLabelRenderer : LabelRenderer
    {
        public MyProjLabelRenderer(Context context) : base(context)
        {

        }
```

But cannot override `FastRenderers.LabelRenderer` because it is [internal](https://github.com/xamarin/Xamarin.Forms/blob/master/Xamarin.Forms.Platform.Android/FastRenderers/LabelRenderer.cs).

 When will these be made public?
